(1)
Exchange Place, north side, from and including William, to and including Hanover Streets.
September 20, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
Another view of the rear of the National City Bank. Also shown is construction in progress on the foundation for the new E-story City
Bank Farmers Trust Co. Building.
September 20, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.  NO REPRODUCTIONs. Neg~'11991
(3)
The same, showing only the upper floors of the National City Bank Bldg. Also seen are (left to right) the Bank of New York and Trust Company, and
the National City Buildings.
September 20, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
